WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.500
Start on the exact operational screen for this guide.

00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:05.000
Messaging is for one clear customer action tied to the right record.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.500
Use conversations, templates, sequences, and opt-outs for different communication checks.

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:10.000
Pick the customer conversation that matches the booking or account reason.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.500
Before sending, confirm recipient, consent, booking code, link, and deadline.

00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:15.000
Do not send if consent, recipient, booking status, or message intent is unclear.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:17.500
Send one clear action from the related booking or customer context.
